headline.main: Malaysia: Ambassador's Expulsion Is a Warning to North Korea
headline.print_headline: Malaysia: Ambassador's Expulsion Is a Warning to North Korea

lead_paragraph: Embattled French presidential candidate Francois Fillon delivered a defiant speech to thousands of supporters in central Paris on Sunday, but made no pledge to fight on as pressure from his conservative party mounted on him to step aside.
